The paper discusses the creation of a dataset for sentiment analysis in images, which involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to extract Adjective-Noun Pairs (ANPs) from image forums. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), or multimedia (cs.MM).
